<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance - GC Pro</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0984e3;
            --text: #2d3436;
            --bg: #f4f7f6;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--text);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .icon-box {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 25px;
            color: #636e72;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .loading-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: #eee;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .progress {
            width: 40%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: loading 2s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn-refresh {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #636e72;
            transition: 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-refresh:hover {
            background: #f1f2f6;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes loading {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(250%);
            }
        }

        @keyframes bounce {

            0%,
            20%,
            50%,
            80%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            40% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

            60% {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Mobile Adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-box">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
        <h1>Maintenance</h1>
        <p>Sistem sedang diupdate untuk meningkatkan kinerja. Mohon tunggu sebentar, kami akan segera kembali</p>

        <div class="loading-bar">
            <div class="progress"></div>
        </div>

        <a href="/" class="btn-refresh">Refresh</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>